er\">ライブ実行を確認</a>）の一部です。 <code>onstatechange</code> ハンドラーは現在の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BaseAudioContext/state\" title=\"state\"><code>state</code></a> を、変化するたびにコンソールへログ出力します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>audioCtx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onstatechange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>audioCtx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://webaudio.github.io/web-audio-api/#dom-baseaudiocontext-onstatechange","title":"Web Audio API"}],"query":"api.BaseAudioContext.statechange_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.BaseAudioContext.statechange_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/BaseAudioContext/statechange_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Audio_API/Using_Web_Audio_API\">ウェブ音声 API の使用</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"イベント型","id":"イベント型"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"statechange イベントは、 BaseAudioContext オブジェクトに対して state メンバーが変化したときに発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BaseAudioContext: statechange event","locale":"en-US","na